    <solution>
      <p>
        By inspection,
        we see that <m>\ve{v} = 2 \ve{b}_1 - \ve{b}_2</m>, so that
        <me>
           [\ve{v}]_\basis{B} := \left[ \begin{array}{c} 2 \\  -1
