      <p>
        Also by inspection,
        we see that <m>\ve{w} = -3 \ve{b}_1 + 2 \ve{b}_2</m>, so that
        <me>
          [\ve{v}]_\basis{B} = \left[ \begin{array}{c} -3 \\  2
          \end{array}  \right]
        </me>
      </p>
    </solution>
